        <h1 style="margin-bottom:0">Staff Training Lab 2 - Hitchhikers Guide to the OCF Lab</h1>
        
        <p>Facilitator: <a href="/staff#ben-cuan">Ben Cuan</a></p>
        
        
        6 min read
        
